Welcompose 0.8.0
================

 * Database: Unique key around fields page and name of table content_boxes
   added; see ticket:6. (andreas) 
 * Database: Fields alternate_title, description and optional_text to 
   content_pages added; see ticket:9. (andreas)
 * Database: sitemap_priority and sitemap_changefreq to content_pages added;
   see ticket:15. (andreas)
 * Core: PEAR::Net_URL from URL generator removed; see ticket:2. (andreas) 
 * Admin: Shockwave flash and windows media video to list of video types
   added; windows media audio to list of audio types added; see ticket:16.
   (andreas)
 * Database: content_simple_forms.type from ENUM to VARCHAR changed; see 
   ticket:13. (andreas)
 * Core: Speed up of class loading in Base_Base; see ticket:3. (andreas)
 * Core: Speed up of class loading using dynamic function calls in the loader;
   see ticket:1. (andreas)
